<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/328914-at-the-end-of-the-book-father-michael">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[At the end of the book Father Michael receives a gift from Grace (Shay's sister). It was a photograph of Michael with his grandfather. The picture supposedly was stolen. What puzzles me is how did Shay have the picture? What did I miss? HELP! <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
