<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/25558172-vivian"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1533437038i/25558172._UX100_CR0,22,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/25558172-vivian">Vivian</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    Shay robbed Michael's dorm room in college. He stole the picture, three packs of Bazooka bubble gum (remember how that one piece of gum was enough for<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Shay robbed Michael's dorm room in college. He stole the picture, three packs of Bazooka bubble gum (remember how that one piece of gum was enough for seven people), and The Gospel Of Thomas from the Nag Hammadi Library. Shay memorized the page; he quoted it to Michael. Shay most likely knew exactly who Michael was when he first visited the prison.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</span>
